1. Use up to date data for displaying
2. Use images with permission for using
3. Add link/button for the feedback
4. Include a link to the privacy policy, add terms and conditions
5. Testing the App (Unit test, UI test, TestFlight)
6. Metadata: make screenshots, app preview, app description and other info that needed to upload the app to the AppStore
7. Sign-up/register in Apple developer program
8. Add app to the iTunes Connect
